New information security web log:

InfoSec News Blog aggregates information and news from 30+ security
related RSS feeds.  Only the best and most interesting make it.  Updated
daily.

http://infosec.volubis.com/

Categories include the information security aspects of:
* Business
* Encryption
* Government
* Legal / Law
* Hacks, Worms, Bugs
* Social Engineering
* Wireless
* General InfoSec News

The blog is very slashdot-like in that much of the content is hyperlinked
to associated news sources and each post includes several links to similar
articles.

Please reply with any submissions, or syndicate the site via Bloglines.

